+ I Test (Restart) All (Iconic) Test ($[FVWM_USERDIR]/icon.tmp.$[w.id].png) WindowStyle IconOverride, Icon $[FVWM_USERDIR]/icon.tmp.$[w.id].png
+ I Module FvwmCommandS
